text: @UPSHelp 801652325194538091  Why has my package been stuck in Richmond, CA since 9/19?

@4citkane I show this is a UPS Mail Innovations package. This is a service your shipper has chosen. UPS Mail Innovations works with the U.S. Postal Service, providing the pick-up, processing, and interim transportation of mail, with final delivery being made by USPS.  1/2 ..
@4citkane 2/2 ..  The package was transferred to USPS on 9/19/18. If you have no received the package you will want to reach out to the shipper on this. ^WS
